# =============================================================================
# .env.example — Nikola AI
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values when later sprints
# introduce configuration that needs secrets (LLM API keys, etc.).
# `.env` itself is gitignored and must NEVER be committed.
#
# Sprint 1 scope: no configuration values are consumed by the application
# yet. This file exists now so the documented pattern (and the .gitignore
# rule protecting it) is established before any secret-bearing config lands.
# =============================================================================

# Example of what a future sprint will add here (NOT used yet):
# NIKOLA_BRAIN_PROVIDER=claude
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=
